lead_paragraph: Bayern Munich's perfect start to the season under coach Carlo Ancelotti came to an end as Jannick Carrasco's first-half goal gave Atletico Madrid a 1-0 home victory in their Champions League Group D game on Wednesday.

headline.print_headline: Carrasco Strike Helps Atletico to Halt Bayern's Perfect Run
headline.main: Carrasco Strike Helps Atletico to Halt Bayern's Perfect Run
